712
00:33:52,990 --> 00:33:54,320
Of course experiences are important.

713
00:33:55,950 --> 00:33:58,980
If you want to express the breadth of life,

714
00:33:59,010 --> 00:33:59,980
or its depth,

715
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,580
