00:41:14,120 --> 00:41:14,990
Delicious and affordable!

835
00:41:15,950 --> 00:41:18,030
You won't gain weight after eating!

836
00:41:18,070 --> 00:41:19,360
Come and check it out.

837
00:41:20,170 --> 00:41:21,980
Miss, would you like some?

838
00:41:22,470 --> 00:41:23,510
Give me ten of these.

839
00:41:23,530 --> 00:41:24,370
Alright!

840
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:25,800
-Please have a seat over there.
-Bring them to me when they're ready.

841
00:41:25,830 --> 00:41:26,270
Okay.

842
00:41:26,310 --> 00:41:27,540
No problem, go ahead.

843
00:41:29,830 --> 00:41:31,550
Aromatic and spicy.

844
00:41:38,710 --> 00:41:40,320
Miss, your skewers are ready.

845
00:41:41,680 --> 00:41:42,530
Thanks.

846
00:42:13,250 --> 00:42:16,500
You ordered so many skewers. Are they good?

847
00:42:18,500 --> 00:42:20,630
I've eaten all over the country,

848
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:22,500
but I've never had anything this delicious.

849
00:42:22,970 --> 00:42:25,080
I can't sleep if I don't eat it for two days.

850
00:42:28,600 --> 00:42:32,130
[Lover's Tears]

851
00:42:30,050 --> 00:42:32,390
I want ten skewers.

852
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:34,830
Do you want regular ones

853
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,440
or Lover's Tears?

854
00:42:37,430 --> 00:42:39,840
What is Lover's Tears?

855
00:42:40,030 --> 00:42:42,230
Lover's Tears is what that gentleman ordered.

856
00:42:42,260 --> 00:42:43,230
It's called Lover's Tears.

857
00:42:46,830 --> 00:42:49,130
Is Lover's Tears good?

858
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:51,350
Would someone as extraordinary as me

859
00:42:51,380 --> 00:42:53,410
eat ordinary things?

860
00:42:55,120 --> 00:42:55,760
Alright!

861
00:42:56,960 --> 00:42:58,460
Give me ten skewers of Lover's Tears.

862
00:42:58,490 --> 00:42:59,330
Alright!

863
00:42:59,390 --> 00:43:02,390
You're also from the Martial Arts World, aren't you?

864
00:43:03,190 --> 00:43:04,730
You're very forthright.

865
00:43:05,320 --> 00:43:06,430
I like it.

866
00:43:08,270 --> 00:43:09,570
You also work and live here?

867
00:43:11,680 --> 00:43:12,790
I'm just passing by.

868
00:43:12,830 --> 00:43:14,360
If it weren't for the delicious food here,

869
00:43:14,380 --> 00:43:15,830
I would have left days ago.

870
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:22,390
So you're also from the Martial Arts World, right?

871
00:43:23,280 --> 00:43:24,690
Then we must have a drink together.

872
00:43:25,520 --> 00:43:27,300
Okay, I'll go buy some wine.

873
00:43:27,340 --> 00:43:28,070
No need, no need.

874
00:43:28,510 --> 00:43:29,930
No need to bother.

875
00:43:30,200 --> 00:43:31,250
They have wine here.

876
00:43:33,970 --> 00:43:34,910
Boss.

877
00:43:35,280 --> 00:43:37,000
That wine you have here,

878
00:43:37,550 --> 00:43:39,110
what's it called again... Something Tears?

879
00:43:39,290 --> 00:43:40,070
Give me a jar of that.

880
00:43:40,400 --> 00:43:41,270
Okay, okay.

881
00:43:43,750 --> 00:43:44,710
Here you are.

882
00:43:44,710 --> 00:43:46,270
Tears of Lovers.

883
00:43:46,870 --> 00:43:47,550
Okay.

884
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:49,080
-Enjoy. Enjoy.
-Go.

885
00:43:55,430 --> 00:43:56,140
Come on.

886
00:43:57,530 --> 00:43:58,410
Cheers, bro.

887
00:44:02,010 --> 00:44:02,790
Come on.

888
00:44:13,490 --> 00:44:16,950
What wine is this? It tastes so awful.

889
00:44:17,770 --> 00:44:19,470
A kindred spirit, I see.

890
00:44:22,410 --> 00:44:24,080
The flavor is quite mellow and fragrant.

891
00:44:24,890 --> 00:44:26,750
You look like a real man.

892
00:44:26,860 --> 00:44:28,550
Why are you acting like those pretentious folks?

893
00:44:29,550 --> 00:44:30,590
Talking nonsense.

894
00:44:30,810 --> 00:44:33,420
You're absolutely right, sir.

895
00:44:33,450 --> 00:44:36,530
Don't be fooled by his manly appearance.

896
00:44:36,560 --> 00:44:40,060
He's actually quite pretentious.

897
00:44:41,550 --> 00:44:43,140
Those pretentious people say

898
00:44:43,240 --> 00:44:45,870
this wine has the fragrance of mountains and the wilderness.

899
00:44:45,900 --> 00:44:47,070
That's just nonsense.

900
00:44:47,210 --> 00:44:48,700
The mountains stink.

901
00:44:48,720 --> 00:44:49,950
There's no fragrance at all.

902
00:44:50,460 --> 00:44:51,350
Right, right.

903
00:44:52,540 --> 00:44:53,660
Kindred spirits.

904
00:44:55,020 --> 00:44:56,030
Kindred spirits indeed.

905
00:45:03,470 --> 00:45:04,860
Your stronghold is still here.

906
00:45:04,890 --> 00:45:06,590
We bought this place to begin with.

907
00:45:06,970 --> 00:45:08,390
We're not enemies now.

908
00:45:08,510 --> 00:45:09,750
There's no need for me to hide it from you.

909
00:45:10,180 --> 00:45:10,830
Alright then.

910
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:12,200
I'll go find Qing Cai.

911
00:45:12,220 --> 00:45:13,510
Let's meet here later.

912
00:45:14,050 --> 00:45:14,870
Okay.

913
00:45:19,590 --> 00:45:20,510
Master.

914
00:45:23,040 --> 00:45:23,710
Sit.

915
00:45:28,110 --> 00:45:30,750
I heard the Ding brothers from back then didn't die.

916
00:45:31,140 --> 00:45:33,630
I've come specifically to deal with them this time.

917
00:45:34,330 --> 00:45:35,670
They've been really rampant.

918
00:45:35,690 --> 00:45:37,350
Even a big shot from Mingyi Manor

919
00:45:37,370 --> 00:45:38,430
has been killed by them.

920
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:42,510
Old Devil Ding's poison is their only real threat.

921
00:45:43,110 --> 00:45:44,430
As for Old Weirdo Ding,

922
00:45:44,500 --> 00:45:46,830
he almost got killed by Yinniang back then.

923
00:45:47,030 --> 00:45:49,610
His martial arts skills are no longer what they used to be.

924
00:45:50,240 --> 00:45:52,420
As it happens, I'm not afraid of poison.

925
00:45:52,660 --> 00:45:54,130
I'm the perfect counter to them.

926
00:45:54,280 --> 00:45:58,280
With the help of the experts the General sent to assist,

927
00:45:59,120 --> 00:46:01,570
dealing with them will be no problem.

928
00:46:02,050 --> 00:46:03,300
Master, you're certainly formidable.

929
00:46:03,630 --> 00:46:05,910
But please be very careful.

930
00:46:05,960 --> 00:46:06,840
Don't worry.

931
00:46:07,690 --> 00:46:09,720
My martial arts skills were on par

932
00:46:09,740 --> 00:46:10,710
with Old Weirdo Ding's back then.

933
00:46:11,390 --> 00:46:13,880
Now, my martial arts skills have improved.

934
00:46:14,520 --> 00:46:16,540
I'll go with you then, Master.

935
00:46:16,610 --> 00:46:18,060
Your current mission

936
00:46:18,330 --> 00:46:20,600
is to protect your lover.

937
00:46:20,850 --> 00:46:23,280
Leave the rest to me.
